QuestData.Title: Wrap it Up
QuestData.Description:
<The seems quite excited about the presence of the new egg. You get the sense that this is an important occasion for these murlocs--there may be few eggs left.
The oracle waves a small piece of seaweed in front of you, showing you the young buds of the immature plant.
She warps the seaweed around a small part of the egg, then points at you, then back at the wrapped seaweed.
It appears that the egg needs to be wrapped in more immature seaweed stalks.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect a Warm Seaweed Stalk, a Young Seaweed Stalk, and a Bulbous Seaweed Stalk and deliver them to the Glimmerfin Oracle.
